	(text "Rx Math (1:1 Impedance Ratio):\n\n    Rsource​=50Ω\n\n    Rswitch​= close to zero\n\n    Rtotal​=50Ω\n\n    N=1\n\n    Effective R for bandwidth: N x R = 50 ohm\n    \n    BW = 1 / (2* pi * N * Reff * C)\n\n    For 96 kHz BW: C= 1 / (2 * pi * 4 * 85 * 96000)​ =  33nF"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
